ll-for-the-first-time-since-2007-3804556">自 2007 年以来在 When 首次完整表演了《The Black Parade》。我们年轻的节日</a>。</p><p>该乐队最新的作品是 2022 年的《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-my-chemical-romances-new-song-the-foundations-of-decay-lyrics-listen-3224304">The Foundations of Decay</a> 》，这是一首令人惊喜的单曲，标志着他们八年来的首张新专辑，他们的最后一张完整专辑是 2010 年的《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/reviews-my-chemical-romance-11724-322210">Danger Days</a> 》。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/my-chemical-romance-share-cryptic-post-if-you-could-be-anything-what-would-you-be-3811721">《我的化学浪漫》帖子分享了一个神秘的帖子：“如果你可以成为任何人，你会成为什么？”</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
丹尼尔·戴-刘易斯拒绝了《吸血鬼访谈》：“他不想拍吸血鬼电影” https://www.nme.com/news/film/daniel-day-lewis-turned-down-interview-with-the-vampire-he-didnt-want-to-do-a-vampire-film-3811709？乌特m_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=丹尼尔·戴·刘易斯拒绝了吸血鬼访谈，他不想拍吸血鬼电影Elizabeth AubreyMon, 11 Nov 2024 21:50:10 +0000 Film NewsNews https://www.nme.com/?p=3811709 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Daniel-Day-Lewis-Photo-by-Kristina-Bumphrey_Variety-via-Getty-Images.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="丹尼尔·戴·刘易斯" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Daniel-Day-Lewis-Photo-by-Kristina-Bumphrey_Variety-via-Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Daniel-Day-Lewis-Photo-by-Kristina-Bumphrey_Variety-via-Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Daniel-Day-Lewis-Photo-by-Kristina-Bumphrey_Variety-via-Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Daniel-Day-Lewis-Photo-by-Kristina-Bumphrey_Variety-via-Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Daniel-Day-Lewis-Photo-by-Kristina-Bumphrey_Variety-via-Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Daniel-Day-Lewis-Photo-by-Kristina-Bumphrey_Variety-via-Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>戴-刘易斯最初被考虑出演莱斯特这个角色</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/daniel-day-lewis-turned-down-interview-with-the-vampire-he-didnt-want-to-do-a-vampire-film-3811709">丹尼尔·戴-刘易斯拒绝《吸血鬼访谈》的帖子：“他不想拍吸血鬼电影”</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Daniel-Day-Lewis-Photo-by-Kristina-Bumphrey_Variety-via-Getty-Images.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="丹尼尔·戴·刘易斯" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Daniel-Day-Lewis-Photo-by-Kristina-Bumphrey_Variety-via-Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Daniel-Day-Lewis-Photo-by-Kristina-Bumphrey_Variety-via-Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Daniel-Day-Lewis-Photo-by-Kristina-Bumphrey_Variety-via-Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Daniel-Day-Lewis-Photo-by-Kristina-Bumphrey_Variety-via-Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Daniel-Day-Lewis-Photo-by-Kristina-Bumphrey_Variety-via-Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Daniel-Day-Lewis-Photo-by-Kristina-Bumphrey_Variety-via-Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>根据对导演尼尔·乔丹的采访，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/daniel-day-lewis">丹尼尔·戴-刘易斯</a>拒绝了<i>《夜访吸血鬼》</i>中的一个角色。</p><p>在庆祝该片由<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/tom-cruise">汤姆·克鲁斯</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/brad-pitt">布拉德·皮特</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kirsten-dunst">克尔斯滕·邓斯特</a>主演的电影上映 30 周年之际，乔丹在接受<a href="https://variety.com/2024/film/features/interview-with-the-vampire-tom-cruise-brad-pitt-neil-jordan-1236205381/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><i>《综艺》杂志</i></a>采访时透露，戴-刘易斯曾被考虑出演莱斯特一角，最终由克鲁斯出演。</p><p>他解释说：“工作室提到了丹尼尔，但我从来不觉得他会这么做。我确实把剧本发给了他，不出所料，他说他不想拍吸血鬼电影。所以提到了很多人。</p><p> “安妮[赖斯，这部电影所依据的书的作者]特别喜欢的是像鲁特格尔·哈尔和杰里米·艾恩斯这样的伟大人物，但我们经历了正常的选角过程，然后有人建议汤姆·克鲁斯。我去见了汤姆两次，然后我想我可以在这里得到一些非常好的东西。我一直很钦佩汤姆作为一名演员，但除了他是当时最炙手可热的明星这一事实之外。” </p><figure id="attachment_3811713" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3811713" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3811713" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Tom-Cruise-and-Brad-Pitt-star-in-Interview-with-the-Vampire_-The-Vampire-Chronicles.-Photo-by-Francois-Duhamel_Sygma-via-Getty-Images.jpg" alt="汤姆·克鲁斯和布拉德·皮特主演《夜访吸血鬼：吸血鬼编年史》" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Tom-Cruise-and-Brad-Pitt-star-in-Interview-with-the-Vampire_-The-Vampire-Chronicles.-Photo-by-Francois-Duhamel_Sygma-via-Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Tom-Cruise-and-Brad-Pitt-star-in-Interview-with-the-Vampire_-The-Vampire-Chronicles.-Photo-by-Francois-Duhamel_Sygma-via-Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Tom-Cruise-and-Brad-Pitt-star-in-Interview-with-the-Vampire_-The-Vampire-Chronicles.-Photo-by-Francois-Duhamel_Sygma-via-Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Tom-Cruise-and-Brad-Pitt-star-in-Interview-with-the-Vampire_-The-Vampire-Chronicles.-Photo-by-Francois-Duhamel_Sygma-via-Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Tom-Cruise-and-Brad-Pitt-star-in-Interview-with-the-Vampire_-The-Vampire-Chronicles.-Photo-by-Francois-Duhamel_Sygma-via-Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Tom-Cruise-and-Brad-Pitt-star-in-Interview-with-the-Vampire_-The-Vampire-Chronicles.-Photo-by-Francois-Duhamel_Sygma-via-Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3811713" class="wp-caption-text">汤姆·克鲁斯和布拉德·皮特主演《夜访吸血鬼：吸血鬼编年史》——图片来源：Francois Duhamel/Sygma via Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>戴-刘易斯最近确认，他将出演儿子<em>Anemone 执导的电影，这</em>是他自 2017 年《魅影缝匠》上映前<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/daniel-day-lewis-acting-retirement-2090803">宣布退休</a>以来的第一个角色<em>。</em>为此，戴-刘易斯获得了<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/oscars">奥斯卡</a>提名。</p><p>戴-刘易斯当时在接受<a href="https://www.wmagazine.com/story/exclusive-daniel-day-lewis-giving-up-acting-phantom-thread" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《W》杂志</em></a>采访时公开了他退休的决定。 “我害怕使用‘艺术家’这个被过度使用的词，但艺术家的责任感笼罩着我，”他解释道。 “我需要相信我正在做的事情的价值。这项工作似乎至关重要。甚至无法抗拒。如果观众相信，那对我来说就足够了。但最近，情况并非如此。”</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/is-daniel-day-lewis-coming-out-of-retirement-3798727">最近有进一步的猜测称，戴-刘易斯可能会永远复出，在他被发现与肖恩·宾一起拍摄电影后，谣言四起。</a></p><p>今年早些时候有报道称， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/daniel-day-lewis-gives-update-on-acting-retirement-3596851">戴-刘易斯仍然坚定地“不再”演戏，</a>电影制片人吉姆·谢里丹告诉<a href="https://www.screendaily.com/news/jim-sheridan-the-whole-film-industry-is-in-the-emergency-room/5191166.article" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《ScreenDaily》</em></a> ：“我一直在和他说话。我很想再次和他一起做某事。他和其他人一样。他打开彩带，有七千个选择，没有一个是好的。”</p><p>然而，据报道，戴-刘易斯现在有人看到他和比恩在曼彻斯特骑摩托车拍摄场景。这部电影被认为被称为<em>《艾芙琳》，</em>比恩被认为在其中扮演一名退伍军人。目前尚不清楚戴刘易斯扮演什么角色。</p><p>一月份，戴-刘易斯还罕见地公开露面于国家评论委员会颁奖典礼上，向他的<em>《纽约黑帮》</em>导演<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/martin-scorsese">马丁·斯科塞斯</a>致敬。</p><p>据<a href="https://variety.com/2024/film/awards/martin-scorsese-daniel-day-lewis-reunite-national-board-review-1235869257/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《综艺》</em></a>报道，这位电影制作人在演讲中调侃了这位演员重返演艺圈，并感谢戴-刘易斯为他颁奖。 “我们一起拍了两部电影，我必须说，这是我一生中最伟大的经历之一。也许还有时间再做一件事。或许！他是最好的。” </p><div id="adm-inline-article-ad-x-8" class="admz "><div class="adma boomerang " data-device="Desktop" data-width="300"><div class="pmc-adm-boomerang-pub-div ad-text" data-priority="10"></div></div></div><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/daniel-day-lewis-turned-down-interview-with-the-vampire-he-didnt-want-to-do-a-vampire-film-3811709">丹尼尔·戴-刘易斯拒绝《吸血鬼访谈》的帖子：“他不想拍吸血鬼电影”</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
 Boom Leeds 确认将于 2025 年 3 月关门https://www.nme.com/news/music/boom-leeds-confirms-it-will-close-its-doors-in-march-2025-3811700?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=boom-leeds-confirms-它将于 2025 年 3 月关门Emma WilkesMon, 11 Nov 2024 21:29:08 +0000 Music NewsNewsHardcoreLive Music NewsPunkRockhttps://www.nme.com/?p=3811700 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/NME-BREAKING-NEWS-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="NME 突发新闻" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/NME-BREAKING-NEWS-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/NME-BREAKING-NEWS-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/NME-BREAKING-NEWS-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/NME-BREAKING-NEWS-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/NME-BREAKING-NEWS-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/NME-BREAKING-NEWS-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这个深受喜爱的可容纳 250 人的场馆对于利兹的硬核音乐界至关重要，但近年来面临着无数威胁</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/boom-leeds-confirms-it-will-close-its-doors-in-march-2025-3811700">Boom Leeds 确认将于 2025 年 3 月关闭的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/NME-BREAKING-NEWS-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="NME 突发新闻" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/NME-BREAKING-NEWS-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/NME-BREAKING-NEWS-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/NME-BREAKING-NEWS-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/NME-BREAKING-NEWS-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/NME-BREAKING-NEWS-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-